                                                <li>Generate transcriptions, tags, and summaries</li>
                                                <li>Provide search and organization features</li>
                                                <li>Create thumbnails and preview images</li>
                                                <li>Perform sentiment and content categorization</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="accordion-item">
                                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
